<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>structs</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>`structs`<sp/>module<sp/>provides<sp/>fundamental<sp/>data<sp/>structures<sp/>used<sp/>throughout<sp/>the<sp/>codebase.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>Key<sp/>Files:</highlight></codeline>
