<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`structs/include/structs/enums.h`:<sp/>Contains<sp/>enumerations<sp/>used<sp/>for<sp/>type<sp/>identification</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`structs/include/structs/model.h`:<sp/>Defines<sp/>structures<sp/>for<sp/>model<sp/>configuration</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>Main<sp/>Components:</highlight></codeline>
